{"tid":2479593,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「爆笑」中金公司合規總監陳剛出軌下屬女同事 錄音被綠帽男用老婆微信發中金高管群","createTime":"2021-04-08T02:10:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-08T02:27:48.000Z","uid":313615,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3bbfbf4bb0b63e095709f7abd02f68f62be9062d","tid":2479593,"uid":313615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T02:10:52.000Z","msg":"中金公司合規總監陳剛出軌下屬女同事。女同事老公同陳剛傾計，陳剛承認出軌男子嘅老婆馬某，話會同馬某結婚，善待其仔。多數時間，男子講嘢有理有節噉問，陳剛都係不緊不慢噉答。<br />\n當陳剛話，&ldquo;請你多擔待。&rdquo;男子話：&ldquo;你瞓咗我老婆，仲要我多擔待？&rdquo;<br />\n錄音被男子用老婆微信發中金高管群<br />\n說話人1就係原配老公李某，說話人2係奸夫陳剛律師，CICC高管。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUdRyUETJt2Szo1QtFnMokckPqQodZrqCnGVDqv4KQYiy?filename=8EpkMW2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8EpkMW2.png&h=fd2ea0db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n錄音流傳，網友翻譯<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmdr8VxNPvbpGYf79CsoKjzwmjt6Gh1uE2U1U7QzdnwBaT?filename=nuA4ubv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnuA4ubv.png&h=f3011510&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZM8jW5kDGa5HfhXx6NotNVvFcNBtQM9YZfYyNhVHcXHK?filename=1tJhPbv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1tJhPbv.png&h=f54a9087&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmavEXNdnkxQpqo5ykYPRpvFSGVJNjcAGfp15bR8tUYbtZ?filename=UMjMHwv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUMjMHwv.png&h=dd03493d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNTFzaWPsWzzA8oRcqdHW22CRUvJZB5eALBwmZFKsnSyz?filename=t817rYa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft817rYa.png&h=384b9883&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQRSquGo52RsMJCVHAwAYpZ1wVUxFTeDS6ctyizLCotRV?filename=d1S6Hwv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd1S6Hwv.png&h=9f17f0a2&s={SIZE}\